        "Name" : "The MechWarrior Code",
        "Details" : "Raised voices echo down the barracks hallway and you arrive to find [[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]] facing off with [[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]].\r\n\r\n\"That's just not how it's done!\" {TGT_MW.Callsign} says. \"We may be mercenaries, but we shouldn't have abandoned the Gwydion Company like that.\"\r\n\r\n\"You're right, we <i>are</i> mercenaries. We go where the money is.\" {SCN_MW.Callsign} sneers. \"You'd rather that we'd faced that Steiner kill team?!? One of US could be dead instead.\"\r\n\r\n{TGT_MW.Callsign} erupts. \"<i>My cousin</i>  was in the Gwydion Company, and he was a better MechWarrior than YOU'LL ever be!\" {TGT_MW.SUBJ_C} {TGT_MW.Gender?NonBinary:stalk|Default:stalks} from the barracks.\r\n\r\nIn the silence that follows, the room finally notices that you've arrived.",
